                                    (default: 50)
      --mel                         Maximum Exon Length. Only impacts --novelSS behavior (int)
                                    (default: 500)

    Other:
      --test                        For running trim test (bool)
                                    To run the first half of the pipeline (through STAR), set test = true.
                                    (default: false)
